[14:16:37.546] [INFO ]     As of the latest policy update on **March 15, 2024**, NovaAI provides new hires with a **one-time home office equipment stipend of $1,500 USD** (or local currency equivalent) to support remote work setup.
    
    This stipend can be used for approved expenses such as:
    - Ergonomic chairs
    - Desks or standing desk converters
    - Monitors, keyboards, or mice
    - Webcams or headsets
    - Other office essentials (with prior approval)
    
    New hires receive the stipend after completing their first 30 days of employment and submitting receipts via the **Expensify** platform. The policy applies to all full-time employees (excluding interns and contractors).
    
    For the most current details, refer to the **NovaAI Employee Handbook (Section 4.3: Remote Work Policy)** or contact **HR@novaai.com**.
