[20:29:34.247] [INFO ]     At NovaAI, the on-call compensation rate is as follows:
    
    - **Standard On-Call Rate**: $50 per hour for hours spent actively responding to incidents while on call.
    - **Standby On-Call Rate**: $2 per hour for hours spent on standby (i.e., available but not actively responding to incidents).
    
    This policy applies to all eligible employees as outlined in the **NovaAI On-Call Policy (v3.2, last updated March 15, 2024)**. Employees in roles requiring on-call duties (e.g., Site Reliability Engineers, DevOps, and certain Support roles) are covered under this policy.
    
    For more details, refer to the **NovaAI Employee Handbook (Section 7.4)** or reach out to **HR@novaai.com**.
